(6008, 189747, 'Crush It', '日本搖滾傳說LUNA SEA吉他手INORAN與在日本也頗具知名度的英國名團FEEDER日裔貝斯手Taka Hirose共組的跨國組合Muddy Apes，以「盡情作出自己想作的搖滾」為最高原則，召集了同樣也是FEEDER的支援吉他手DEAN TIDEY以及大阪異色搖滾團8otto主唱MAESON一同共襄盛舉，首張作品『Crush It!』完全在美國進行製作，並邀來曾為U2、pulp、Elton John、Paul McCartnry等大咖合作的英國製作人Steve Orchard擔綱錄音工程，交出一張名符其實放諸世界標準皆毫不遜色的搖滾佳作！', '2013-08-20 00:00:00', 0, 1, 1, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2013-08-12 17:51:54', '2015-02-16 15:48:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6009, 189747, 'FAIRY DIRT No. 5', '以INORAN(LUNA SEA)、Taka Hirose（FEEDER）為首的跨國搖滾勁旅Muddy Apes繼首張作品『Crush It!』後僅相隔一年便再接再厲推出第二張專輯『FAIRY DIRT No.5』。僅僅花了三週時間便完成的此作，卻絲毫沒有妥協，純熟洗鍊的厚實搖滾聲線展現出老將的堅強穩定度與實力。\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n☆★ Song List               \r\n1.	New Sunday\r\n2.	KIZUNA DRIVE\r\n3.	Beautiful Drunk\r\n4.	Tequila No.5\r\n5.	Space Monkey\r\n6.	Peep Show\r\n7.	Terasu Karma\r\n8.	Angel,Devil Booom\r\n9.	Generation 555\r\n', '2013-08-20 00:00:00', 0, 1, 1, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2013-08-12 18:13:08', '2015-02-16 15:48:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6010, 110503, '若是有一蕊號作正義的花', '\r\n整張專輯由Chthonic閃靈的鍵盤手CJ擔任製作人，從錄音、混音到後製全程操盤。　「正義」往往使人聯想到一朵綻放的花，不過火燒島這張「若是有一蕊號作正義的花」專輯的主軸卻是放在「這朵花的土壤是什麼？」　這片土壤蘊含著各種悲傷、憤怒、徬徨與無助，同時卻也存在著堅韌的意志與崇高的理想。歌曲的脈絡針對不當的開發、對於核能存有蒼白的美好幻想到對於戰爭的疑惑、威權時代的刑求與現實權力的綑綁，這一切都是我們眼中所見，而我們卻總是期待著有一天看到那朵叫作公理與正義的花綻放，忽略了我們其實就是土壤，也是這朵花的種子。', '2013-03-29 00:00:00', 0, 1, 9, 'CJ Studio', '', 0, '', 0, 1, '2013-08-13 04:58:31', '2013-08-13 05:21:39', '2013-08-13 05:21:39'),
(6011, 110503, '若是有一蕊號作正義的花', '發行於2013，整張專輯由Chthonic閃靈的鍵盤手CJ擔任製作人，從錄音、混音到後製全程操盤。　「正義」往往使人聯想到一朵綻放的花，不過火燒島這張「若是有一蕊號作正義的花」專輯的主軸卻是放在「這朵花的土壤是什麼？」　這片土壤蘊含著各種悲傷、憤怒、徬徨與無助，同時卻也存在著堅韌的意志與崇高的理想。歌曲的脈絡針對不當的開發、對於核能存有蒼白的美好幻想到對於戰爭的疑惑、威權時代的刑求與現實權力的綑綁，這一切都是我們眼中所見，而我們卻總是期待著有一天看到那朵叫作公理與正義的花綻放，忽略了我們其實就是土壤，也是這朵花的種子。\n\nBlossom of Roaring Justice\n\n“Burning Island”, formed in 2011, composed of five teenagers born and raised in Taiwan, has been performing at numerous live houses around the island and has also been invited to sing at major music festivals like Mega Port Festival、Spring Scream etc. in the year after its formation. The music from Burning Island consists of voices in the southern Taiwanese accent along with straightforward Heavy Metal Riffs, strong-tempo drum beats and a heavy Bass line, all contributing to a unique Southern style of Heavy metal. As to the contents, Burning Island focuses mainly on social issues, mixed up with angers and hatred, and innumerable doubts and cautions against the unknown and presents them in lyrics using copious metaphor, sometimes colloquial, sometimes in imaginative rhyming, and weaving it all into strong Heavy metal music, making them quite thought-provoking. The full album was solely produced by Cj ,the Keyboard player of “Chthonic” , who did mixing and mastering. ”Justice” always reminds us of a flower in full blossom. However, the purpose of the album ”Blossom of Roaring Justice” dwells on the question of “ What is the soil the flower planted in?”. The soil contains all sorts of sorrows、angers、hesitations and helplessness, coexisting with strong wills and lofty ideals at the same time. The contexts of the various tracks are aimed at inappropriate exploitation、illusion of the nuclear power、questioning toward wars、tortures from Totalitarianism and the shackling of peoples’ rights. All of these are actually what we see, but still we long for the full blossom of the flower called “Justice”. only to ignore that we are the soil, namely ,the origin of the flower. ', '2013-03-29 00:00:00', 0, 1, 9, 'CJ Studio', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2013-08-13 05:23:57', '2015-02-16 15:48:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
